commit.title: [feedback] [rfc] Remove Feedback Glob output.
commit.message:
[feedback] [rfc] Remove Feedback Glob output.

This is unused by up-to-date IDEs (*), it is also undocumented; IMVHO
its utility is very limited so we may want to clean it up.

IDEs in general do want more detailed information than what is
provided here, and in the typical client/server UI model functionality
such as document symbols has its own request.

(*) PIDEtop used the option tho.
